OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Freturning through the night, which
OL,7,Fcould turn heavy at times during the
OL,8,Fearly morning especially. Winds
OL,9,Fincreasing around coastal areas, but a
OL,10,Fslight frost developing in sheltered
OL,11,Finland spots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FAnother day of sunshine and
OL,14,Fblustery showers, some of the showers
OL,15,Fagain could be heavy with the added
OL,16,Frisk of hail in places. Remaining
OL,17,Fchilly, with temperatures below
OL,18,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
