OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying mixed to end the week with
OL,7,Ffurther sunshine and showers likely.
OL,8,FDrier, with lighter winds to start the
OL,9,Fweekend though. Temperatures staying
OL,10,Fbelow average for the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
